<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>On Sunday he shared some footage of a project he's been shooting for Death Wish skateboards. </p>

<p>And on Tuesday Jason Momoa was repping the brand again, by wearing one of their T-shirts during a lunchtime catch up with friends.</p>

<p>The 41-year-old Aquaman star paired the low-key garment with an unmissable pair of red trousers. </p>

<p>Scroll down to see video </p>

<p>He's a fan: On Tuesday Jason Momoa was repping the Death Wish skateboard brand, by wearing one of their T-shirts during a lunchtime catch up with friends</p>

<p>Jason completed the casual look with flip flops, and made sure to cover his face with a face mask, from his own On The Roam clothing line.</p>

<p>The 6ft4in star shielded his eyes with shades as he enjoyed a relaxing meal with a couple of male friends at LA's Vitalist eatery.</p>

<p>The Game of Thrones star wore his wavy brunette tresses loose and flowing for the outing. </p>

<p>Red-dy or not: The 41-year-old Aquaman star paired the low-key garment with an unmissable pair of red trousers</p>

<p>Behind the scenes: On Sunday the See star slipped behind the camera to film pro skateboarder Erik Ellington</p>

<p>On Sunday the See star slipped behind the camera to film pro skateboarder Erik Ellington.</p>

<p>In a behind-the-scenes video, Jason recorded the 43-year-old performing tricks on a basketball court.</p>

<p>At one point Erik ollied over a construction sign, with Jason skating close behind.</p>

<p>In another video, he showed Ellington land the jump in extreme slow motion.</p>

<p>The in-demand actor will next be seen on screens in Denis Villeneuve's Dune later this year, while the sequel to his mega-success Aquaman has been announced with a 2022 release date anticipated. </p>

